title: #1-6 Thanos: Infinity Abyss (comics)
description:
Six Thanos clones, hybridised with other prominent Marvel Universe figures including Doctor Strange, Professor X and Galactus acting on their template&#039;s nihilistic desire to end the universe, while they were opposed by a group including Adam Warlock, Spider-Man, Doctor Strange and Thanos himself.

A sequel was produced that continued the focus on Thanos, in Marvel Universe: The End.

(Taken from the wikipedia article)


One of my personal favourites. I&#039;ve also got The Infinity Gauntlet and The Infinity War. Soon i will upload Marvel Universe: The End.
